Developer Terms of Use
des:
Becoming a man of sexual integrity in an ongoing process, and we can help you on the journey. New Life Ministries’ EVERY MAN’S BATTLE PODCAST can assist you on the pathway to becoming the man you hope to be. As all things sexual integrity; EVERY MAN’S BATTLE PODCAST is for EVERY MAN!

Once enabled, you can listen to the most recent episode by saying, "Alexa, play Every Man's Battle Podcast"

To pause or resume any episode, say "Alexa, pause" or "Alexa, resume." To listen to previous episodes, say "Alexa, play the previous episode." If you want to know the title of an episode while the episode is playing, say "Alexa, ask Every Man's Battle Podcast for the title of this episode." If you want to know the air date of an episode, say "Alexa, ask Every Man's Battle Podcast for the date of this episode."
